tool_description:
Realtime APIs support entire shopping flow on Target.com.
(Free trial enabled)
title: Target.com Shopping - API

api_list.name: product_details
api_list.description:
Returns detailed product information.
Including:
```
product variants (with different dimension like size, color and etc.
ratings and reviews
item images/videos
price
promotion
child products
```

required_parameters.name: tcin
required_parameters.description:
Target product id.
Value comes from product search API.

required_parameters.name: store_id
required_parameters.description:
The id of the store which product details data is being retrieved from. (Required, CANNOT be empty)
Value comes from nearby store API.

Example: 3330

most_recent.title: Dont. Just dont.

most_recent.title: fits 50" tv great!

most_recent.text: It is better than i thought. I really love it.

bullet_descriptions: Features: Cable/Cord Management, Open Shelves, Adjustable Shelves
Assembly Details: Adult Assembly Required, Some Tools Provided
Compartment 1 Type: Shelf (2): 7.87 Inches (H) x 25.25 Inches (W) x 13.5 Inches (D)
product_description.downstream_description:
Simple is better. That’s why Sophie snatched Saracina Home’s Four Cubby Modern Simple Storage Stand off the web the moment she saw it. She knew she could use this trusty console in her extra guest room as an open concept dresser or bookshelf. Its smooth painted surface looked so nice under the window, and Sophie was thrilled she had transformed her guest room’s empty corner into a chic reading and storage nook. Sophie likes that that four cord management ports helped her keep the console nice and tidy. But most of Sophie liked that she could have placed this storage stand in her living room, kitchen, or home office and would have been just as please with the result. Be like Sophie and shop smarter, not harder.

Additional Dimensions:
• Overall Height: 23.37”
• Overall Width: 58.12”
• Overall Depth: 15.75”
• Shelf Width: 25.25"
• Shelf Clearance (per shelf): 7.87"
• Upper Shelf Depth: 13.50"
• Lower Shelf Depth: 14.12"
product_description.soft_bullet_description:
•Long-lasting MDF wood core
•Open storage for all your organizational needs
•4 cord management ports help keep your unit tidy
•Place in the living room, home office, or dining room
•Use as a console, a TV stand, or as a storage sideboard
•Recommended weight limit: 250 pounds
•Accommodates TVs up to 65 inches
•Assembly is required
